# Runtime-generated snapshots written into the exports volume at request time
# (settings saves, dated settings/timeseries snapshots). Per-deployment runtime
# state, not source. Explicitly-tracked seed files (e.g. exports/headcount.csv)
# stay tracked because they are already committed.
